**Key changes to `baseRaids.ts`:**
- Fixed RNG scope `"raids"` → `"raid"` to match spec
- `generateRaidWave`: parameter renamed `waveNumber` → `dayNumber` (the seed key is now per-day, not per-wave-index)
- `shouldTriggerRaid(dayNight, affectsGameplay)` — gates on `timeOfDay === "night"` + Survival mode flag
- `getApproachDirections(chunkX, chunkZ, worldSeed, dayNumber)` — returns 1-2 cardinal directions, deterministically seeded by chunk position + day

`★ Insight ─────────────────────────────────────`
The chunk coordinates are appended as extra args to `scopedRNG("raid", worldSeed, dayNumber, chunkX, chunkZ)` — the same composable mechanism used throughout the codebase. This gives each chunk a unique approach direction per day without any additional state or coordination across chunks.
